posts.title: How could you vote for Trump? You went to college!
posts.content:
Okay, I happen to have a lot of public school teacher in my family who all vote Democrat. They get furious when they see my pro Trump posts. But the weirdest comment I got was 'How can someone with a college degree vote for someone like him!'

Gee I don't know, maybe its because I had a very liberal professor who constantly defended pedophiles.

Maybe because I had another professor who mocked the black students saying that they couldn't legalize marijuana because then minorities who rely on it in the hood wouldn't be able to get a job. And literally told one of the black students 'I'm just saying your people in certain neighborhoods have a hard time finding opportunity.'

Maybe its because I heard a liberal professor call for a genocide of Trump supporters back in 2016.

And above all else, maybe its because I had a friend of mine killed by some wanna be gang members in a drive by. I KNOW the world isn't a safe place, so I conceal carry. And Liberals want to take that right away.

You may have wanted me to be another brainwashed college liberal, but I've seen through that bullshit

EDIT: And to make matters worse I was a Psychology major so my bachelors degree is pretty much useless, and I got called an evil white man for four years for nothing
